item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

acually they can’t find it 2 ways…

1.Hard Way (Searching That Type Of Model)
They would create a command and then use it until they found that type they are looking for.

2.Easy Way(Dumping That Type Of Model Data)
They make a method that dumps all the data of the client to a file while it loads

i use the 2nd way because its funnier,Thats how i found some of the contruction objects in the 377 client
